            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "No evidence for European bats serving as reservoir for Borna disease virus 1 or other known mammalian orthobornaviruses",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Daniel",
                    "lastName": "Nobach"
